dcterms:description: The Duke DME dataset consists of 110 B-scans from 10 patients suffering from diabetic macular edema (DME). It was collected using the standard Spectralis and includes annotations for three categories: layer, fluid, and background, consisting of 10 classes.
dcterms:title: Duke DME dataset
